trans-unit.source: Represents an assembly reference and the namespace imported from that assembly.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma referência de assembly e o namespace importado desse assembly.

trans-unit.source: This class is used by <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicValue%601> and <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicReference%601> to provide assembly references and namespaces required for expression compilation.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe é usada por <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicValue%601> e <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicReference%601> para fornecer referências de assembly e namespaces necessários à compilação de expressão.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the full name of the assembly referenced by this <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o nome completo do assembly referenciado por esta <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.

trans-unit.source: The full name of the assembly referenced by this <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.
trans-unit.target: O nome completo do assembly referenciado por este <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> to compare with the current <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> a ser comparado com o <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> atual.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> is equal to the current <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.
trans-unit.target: Determina se o <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> especificado é igual ao <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> atual.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> is equal to the current <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> especificado for igual ao <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> atual; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o código hash da instância de <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.

trans-unit.source: The hash code for the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: O código hash da instância de <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the imported namespace referenced by this <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o namespace importado referenciado por esta <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.

trans-unit.source: The imported namespace referenced by this <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.
trans-unit.target: O namespace importado referenciado por este <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.
